Google Web Toolkit Maven Plugin (gwt-maven-plugin)

 The gwt-maven-plugin provides support for {{{http://code.google.com/webtoolkit/}GWT}} projects,
 including running the GWT developer tools (the compiler, shell and i18n generation) and performing
 support operations to help developers make GWT fit more closely in with their standard JEE web
 application development (debugging, managing the embedded server, running noserver, merging web.xml,
 generating I18N interfaces, generating Async GWT-RPC interfaces, and more) and environment (Eclipse IDE).

